data.title: SwiftPaste
data.details: A Chrome extension optimizing text inputs by providing quick access to a categorized text storage, based on context.

data.title: Cooking with Fralle
data.details: Keeping track of my preferred recipes was constantly difficult. Whether I utilized concealed Facebook groups or resorted to browser bookmarks, no method seemed sufficiently effective. The best answer to this issue was to create a self-hosted website with a brief URL for convenient accessibility.
